Wing, scale bar: 0.5 mm. 
<emphasis id="FBE05D5AFFC7FF9DFB6CF89D9F96DA25" bold="true" box="[1204,1224,1894,1918]" pageId="6" pageNumber="446">2.</emphasis>
Spiracular sclerite, scale bar: 0.05 mm. 
<emphasis id="FBE05D5AFFC7FF9DFEABF8719AD8DAF9" bold="true" box="[371,390,1930,1954]" pageId="6" pageNumber="446">3.</emphasis>
Tergite 6, scale bar: 0.1 mm. 
<emphasis id="FBE05D5AFFC7FF9DFD12F8719980DAF9" bold="true" box="[714,734,1930,1954]" pageId="6" pageNumber="446">4.</emphasis>
Tip of abdomen in lateral view, scale bar: 0.1 mm. 
<emphasis id="FBE05D5AFFC7FF9DFAD6F8719E7CDAF9" bold="true" box="[1294,1314,1930,1954]" pageId="6" pageNumber="446">5.</emphasis>
Segment 7 (sternite above), scale bar: 0.1 mm. 
<emphasis id="FBE05D5AFFC7FF9DFDC1F8559973DA9D" bold="true" box="[537,557,1966,1990]" pageId="6" pageNumber="446">6.</emphasis>
Genital capsule in ventral view, scale bar: 0.1 mm. 
<emphasis id="FBE05D5AFFC7FF9DFB83F8559F31DA9D" bold="true" box="[1115,1135,1966,1990]" pageId="6" pageNumber="446">7.</emphasis>
Sperm pump, scale bar: 0.1 mm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption id="9DEBD1C0FFC6FF9CFF4FFD249906DE47" pageId="7" pageNumber="447" startId="7.[151,271,735,759]" targetBox="[156,1430,198,709]" targetPageId="7">
